Is e sgoil ailtireachd Gearamailteach a tha ann an Bauhaus, steidhichte air am posdalaid 
"Is e beart a tha ann an taigh, beart anns a bhios daoine beo."
Is e inneal iom-fhillte a tha ann an "beart", agus is e bun-phrionnsabal de innleadaireachd gum bu choir do ''''dealbh'' a leantainn dleasdanas'' . Nochd an sgoil "bauhaus" re na 1930n, agus aobharaich e  taighean de nós caran cearnach, gun moran sgeadachadh , taobh a muigh neo taobh a-staigh.

